KALSHI PLATFORM MECHANICS & REFERENCE

### Order Types - Technical Details

**Quick Order (Market Order)**
- Executes immediately at best available price
- Can span multiple price levels if quantity exceeds availability at best price
- Platform automatically calculates and displays average fill price
- How to place: Select strike → Choose Yes/No → Enter dollar value OR number of contracts → Execute

**Limit Order**
- Specify maximum price willing to pay (for buys) or minimum price willing to accept (for sells)
- Only executes at specified price or better
- May remain unfilled if market never reaches specified price
- Allows partial fills
- How to place: Enter quantity → Set limit price → Order executes automatically when contracts available at or below your price

