### Selling Positions - Mechanics

- Available anytime before market expiration
- Quick Order: Sells immediately at best available price
- Limit Order: Sells at specified price or higher
- Platform displays: Current position size, estimated payout before execution
- Selling works identically to buying, just in reverse direction

