### Flip Selling - Technical Details

**Mechanics:**
- Sell more contracts than currently owned
- Platform automatically: (1) Sells existing contracts, (2) Buys opposite side contracts to fulfill order
- Net result: Position flips from one side to other

**Example:**
- Current position: 5 No contracts
- Place sell order: 10 No contracts
- Platform executes: Sell 5 No + Buy 5 Yes
- Final position: 5 Yes contracts

**Fee Treatment:**
- Charged trading fees on both legs (sell + buy)
- No special fee treatment for flip selling

